snippet.textDisplay:
As much as I like this theory I am afraid that part between 6:30 to 7:00 is perfect allegory for Bone works game itself and it's main problem. Presentation.

There is in storytelling advice to present audience of any kind with metaphorical 2+2 and allow them to get 4 out of it - it is to create engagement from audience (or players in case of boneworks) with the text of book or movie or game.

However Boneworks hides its story and maybe even the plot so much to get all fans of digging and analysis of lore that for a lot of people desire to engage is just not there. I can say from my own experience (of watching streams of GT live,) that lack of things to engagement beyond gameplay, is so bad I forgot what was took place in game, almost immediately stream ended. It feels like there is no plot (goals-stakes-urgency), it feels like we don't know why things are happening

After seeing that Mark and Jack play only a bit of this game we can see that lack of things to engage beyond gameplay reaches level of problem where players can ask themselves "why should I keep playing this game".

I appreciate all the digging and stitching MatPat and team did for this game - you guys basically are doing the hard work here when comes to putting story into boneworks in such way it works on the smallest minimum. Because game developers of Boneworks did such bad job with it that people don't even see anything worth paying attention to. This game is forgettable.

Arc Angel Gabriel stated to Mr. Duduman; I love this country and the people here but, it is like Sodom and Gomorrah and one day it will burn. He showed him all of California, this is as Sodom and Gomorrah and their sins have reached God and God has decided to punish them by fire. He showed him Las Vegas, and said this is as Sodom and Gomorrah and one day it will burn. He also showed him New York and Florida and said these are as Sodom and Gomorrah and one day they both will burn. Mr. Duduman asked the angel, how can America burn when it’s so powerful? He stated, The Russian spies have figured out where the most powerful nuclear plants are in America and when America thinks it’s peace and safety and they rule the world, then from the oceans out of Cuba, Nicaragua, Central America, Mexico; they will bombard all the nuclear plants in America and America will burn. Mr. Duduman asked the angel, what about the churches in America? The angel responded, “People glorify people, the honor that Christ deserves.” Men take up in church; there is divorce, sodomy, adultery, abortion and all kinds of sin and Christ will not live in sin. Christ lives in holiness. I brought you here to cry out loud and tell them to stop sinning and to repent because God never stops forgiving. For those who repent, God will save them in times of trouble. (A thousand shall fall at thy side, and ten thousand at thy right hand; but it shall not come nigh thee. (Psalms 91:7).

*Arc Angel Gabriel tells Mr. Duduman that the scriptures in Jeremiah Chapters 50 and 51 do not talk about ancient Babylon. It talks about America and I will open up your mind and you will understand. (Babylon hath been a golden cup in the Lord’s hand, that made all the earth drunken. The nations have drunken of her wine; therefore the nations are mad. (Jeremiah 51:7). (American had the word of God in its hand. America had trusted in God. America had missionaries. America spread the gospel though out the world. Many people came to God but, America fell from the truth). (We would have healed Babylon, but she is not healed. (Jeremiah 51:9). (We would have healed America if it would have repented). (O thou that (dwellest upon) many waters, abundant in treasures, thine end is come, and the measure of thy covetousness. (Jeremiah 51:13). (Come out of her, my people, that ye be not partakers of her sins, and that ye receive not of her plagues. (Revelation 18:4). (Because we say we will be taken out of here before any tribulation, and because of that in one day hunger, famine and will be utterly destroyed by fire. Because you say you have God and you say you go to church but, I still smoke and I still divorce and I still drink and I still live like the world does. “And whoever loves the world and the things of the world, the love of the father is not in them.” (1 John 2:15). If you want to have the love of God in your heart, brother you must live your life with God). (Arc Angel Gabriel stated: As God protected Daniel from the lions and from the fiery furnace that is how I will protect my people). All of this has to be fulfilled, so the word of God may come to pass. I pray that we all will make it. When Christ returns, he will take us up, that we will not be left behind.
